{"tid":1411283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗水馬堵路　私家車衝路障　有人擦傷","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T03:28:13.000Z","uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4af531a0f860cbf0503adee71d308c67e1d80e74","tid":1411283,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190805/s00001/bd73ff5be4e1d4a0afd2cd1d73a868d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190805%2Fs00001%2Fbd73ff5be4e1d4a0afd2cd1d73a868d8.jpg&h=939336d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190805/s00001/bd761b73a525817e5b652b86f6202920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190805%2Fs00001%2Fbd761b73a525817e5b652b86f6202920.jpg&h=9f2d8cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190805/s00001/bd760118f170e6aab45a2bfcdc624205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190805%2Fs00001%2Fbd760118f170e6aab45a2bfcdc624205.jpg&h=9ba4ce87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間今日（5日）發起全港罷工，市民於多區路面架設路障堵路。其中，有市民於元朗YOHO對開馬路放置水馬，其間一輛灰色本田汽車停泊於水馬前，記者現場所見，車廂內本來沒人，其後疑有人登車，驅車衝向水馬並往上水方向離開，有市民隨即敲打車窗，欲阻止私家車離開。現場消息稱，在場兩名市民遭私家車擦傷，清醒被送博愛醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n根據車輛登記資料，涉事私家車的登記車主為男子潘X仁，登記地址為大圍祥豐大樓，但公司註冊處未有其記錄。"},{"pid":"a73d3b64a587b08f649889c0413aa6a8c3da96b1","tid":1411283,"uid":4083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"}]}